{"id":551326252,"lang":"java","time":"5 months, 1 week","timestamp":1631079987,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/551326252/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        // brute force\n        int n = s.length();\n        int res = 0;\n        for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){\n            for(int j = 0; j < n; j++){\n                if(check(s,i,j)) res = Math.max(res, j-i+1); // j-i+1 is length of the current substring which ain't got any repeating chars. \n            }\n        }\n        return res;\n    }\n    private boolean check(String s, int start, int end){\n        int[] chars = new int[128];\n        for(int i = start; i <= end; i++){\n            char c = s.charAt(i);\n            chars[c]++;\n            if(chars[c] > 1) return false;\n        }\n        return true;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
